      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780747520299,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "TECH STACK:\n\nFrontend: React + Tailwind CSS\n(for styling) + React Flow (for\ndraggable memory nodes).\n\nBackend: FastAPI (Handling state\nlogic hardcoded via Python\ndictionaries and Pydantic models).\n\nBridge: WebSockets (For real-time,\nstep-by-step streaming of kernel\nevents).\n\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "TECH STACK:\n\nFrontend: React + Tailwind CSS (for styling) + React Flow (for draggable memory nodes).\n\nBackend: FastAPI (Handling state logic hardcoded via Python dictionaries and Pydantic models).\n\nBridge: WebSockets (For real-time, step-by-step streaming of kernel events).\n\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
