      "updated": 1780732280787,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "#KillTheAbstraction is an interactive, web-based\neducational visualizer designed to demystify the\ninvisible mechanics of operating systems. Project\n1 focuses specifically on the Linux Process\nModel and Bash Shell.\n\nInstead of treating the terminal like a black box\nwhere magic text commands are typed, this\nplatform provides a real-time, synchronized split-\nscreen interface. The left pane functions as a\nresponsive Ubuntu terminal emulator, while the\nright pane dynamically visualizes the underlying\nVirtual Memory Space (VMS), process lifecycles\n(fork/exec), and variable inheritance rules. By\ntranslating text commands into physical, spatial,\nand animated memory states, the platform\nbridges the gap between syntax and conceptual\nunderstanding for engineers\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "#KillTheAbstraction is an interactive, web-based educational visualizer designed to demystify the invisible mechanics of operating systems. Project 1 focuses specifically on the Linux Process Model and Bash Shell.\n\nInstead of treating the terminal like a black box where magic text commands are typed, this platform provides a real-time, synchronized split-screen interface. The left pane functions as a responsive Ubuntu terminal emulator, while the right pane dynamically visualizes the underlying Virtual Memory Space (VMS), process lifecycles (fork/exec), and variable inheritance rules. By translating text commands into physical, spatial, and animated memory states, the platform bridges the gap between syntax and conceptual understanding for engineers\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Q1GWiUUmJGqU0j-WD7PjJ",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 120.30701161954781,
      "y": -985.0099991759971,
      "width": 214.10636810563565,
      "height": 144.39728195046283,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
